                     Executive Order 14210, implementing the President’s Department of Government Efficiency Workforce Optimization Initiative and the
                     March 2025 Deputy Secretary of War memorandum. The Air Force conducted comprehensive data-hygiene and manpower-validation
                     efforts, resulting in a correction where FY2026 staffing levels were set below the Flight Training Program established requirements,
                     resulting in a suppressed baseline, which produces a larger year-over-year variance. The FY2027 request reflects the full
