and all of FY 2027. The category naming update from IFT to IPT will be reflected in future budget requests. IFF is transitioning to FBF with Basic and Employment Phases.
The Basic and Employment Phases are both captured in the FY 2026 and FY 2027 numbers. The production requirement estimates represent each of the following
Training Types: Remotely Piloted Aircraft (URT); Air Battle Managers (ABM); Pilot Training (UPT); Combat Systems Officers (CSO); Fighter Bomber Fundamentals (FBF);
Introduction to Fighter Fundamentals (IFF); Introductory Flight Training (IFT) and Initial Pilot Training (IPT).




