           1) Civilian Pay - Enhanced Performance Award Pool for DoW Civilian Employees ..................................................................................... $1,512
           Increase funding strengthens the Department's ability to recognize and reward the civilian workforce whose expertise and continuity
           underpin mission success. Expanded award capacity helps retain the talent that sustains warfighter readiness, drives innovation, and
