                     2) Efficiency - Printing and Reproduction ................................................................................................................................................... $-14,999
                     Reduces funding for printing and reproduction to align with historical execution levels and ensure alignment with the priorities of the
                     Secretary of War to improve the efficiency and effectiveness of our mission and business operations.

                     OP32:
