3) Average Workyear Cost Adjustment ......................................................................................................................................................... $3,705
An increase in funding is required to account for higher average workyear costs driven by expanded use of incentives and special
salary rates needed to recruit and retain mission-critical civilian personnel. These adjustments ensure the Air Force Reserve
maintains a stable, skilled civilian workforce essential to readiness and evolving mission requirements..
