4) Combat Communications LODGET .......................................................................................................................................................... $1,046
This increase provides funding for supplies and materials needed to close the sustainment gap associated with the Logistics Detail
(LOGDET) requirements for three Air Force Reserve Command Combat Communications Squadrons. The funding sustains the
personal protective equipment (PPE) packages required to support worldwide deployment of communications Unit Type Codes
(UTCs). The Air Force Reserve is tasked to provide C4I and C2 systems at deployed locations, and each unit requires consistent
sustainment funding to provide consumable support items and equipment necessary to maintain mission readiness. This increase
ensures Combat Communications units remain fully equipped, deployable, and capable of meeting global operational demands.

