4) Space Warning/Defense - Resilient Operations ................................................................................................................................... $158,718
This specific increase funds supplies and equipment purchases to standup new operation centers and fielding of the new FORGE
system into the overarching portfolio to enhance and modernize the Spaced Based Infrared Systems (SBIRS). The SBIRS are critical
for enhancing the resilience and survivability of our nation's missile warning defense architecture. This system provides essential
early warning for missiles, missile defense, battlespace awareness, and technical intelligence. This funding supports the U.S. Space
Force's investment in resilient operations, critical to combat the increasingly contested and competitive space domain.

