6) Space Superiority - Joint Tactical Ground System ................................................................................................................................. $12,537
Increase for the Joint Tactical Ground System (JTAGS) is essential to bolster the system's capability to deliver timely and precise
missile warning data to ground-based tactical warfighters. By leveraging space-based sensor data, JTAGS provides battlefield
commanders with critical insights into missile launches and emerging threats. This investment will provide for additional software and
hardware maintenance, obsolescence mitigation, sustaining engineering, cybersecurity, field service representatives (on-site tech
support) and software licenses.

