(FY 2026 Base: $17,250)

7) Space Superiority - NAVSTAR Global Positioning System .................................................................................................................... $30,953
Increase for the NAVSTAR GPS is necessary to accelerate the integration of enhanced cybersecurity measures and anti-jamming
capabilities, ensuring uninterrupted GPS availability for military operations in contested environments. GPS provides critical
Positioning, Navigation, and PNT data essential for weapons systems, navigation, and situational awareness for warfighters
worldwide. This investment demonstrates a commitment to maintaining GPS as a resilient and reliable PNT resource, vital for
national security and global stability.

