operations and equipment purchases as well as civilian personnel, Selected Marine Corps Reserve (SMCR), Individual Ready Reserve (IRR), and Individual
Mobilization Augmentees (IMA) support. These resources also support service from Defense Finance and Accounting Service (DFAS), Defense Information
Systems Agency (DISA) and Technology Service Organization (TSO).

The FY 2027 budget request of $9.4 million depicts a total decrease of -$2.4 million from the FY 2026 enacted funding levels, of which $0.1 million is attributed
